## 4. Integration Issue Documentation Rule

When you detect an integration issue, **MUST automatically create** a markdown file.

**Triggers**: HTTP 4xx/5xx errors, data format mismatches, auth failures, WebSocket failures

**File Naming**: `docs/integration_issues/INTEGRATION_ISSUE_[TYPE]_[DESC]_[YYYYMMDD].md`

**Template**: See `.cursor/rules/detailed/integration-issue-documentation.md`

